    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi everyone! Up for grabs is my reliable ride that's been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for its next adventure. Everything runs smoothly, and it looks great inside and out! I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner very happy. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 34500.0,
