    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. The power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip differential. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The suspension geometry remains precise, and the chassis feedback is unfiltered, making it an ideal candidate for a spirited daily driver or weekend canyon car. Mechanically robust with a clean power band and crisp gear engagement.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car for sale. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Reliable daily driver. Ready for pickup.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance and everyday utility. The exterior paint still holds a deep, impressive shine, with only minor road peppering on the front fascia and a small, superficial scuff on the rear passenger door that is only visible under direct light. The alloy wheels are straight and free of major curb rash, wrapped in tires with approximately 70% tread life remaining. Inside, the cabin environment is clean and smoke-free; the leather bolsters show only light natural creasing, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. All interior electronics\u2014including the infotainment screen, heated seats, and backup camera\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, this car is sound. It has been serviced at 5,000-mile intervals, and the engine idles quietly with no fluid leaks or warning lights on the dash. The transmission shifts crisply, and the suspension remains tight over bumps. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner to drive home with confidence.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, which exemplifies a harmonious balance of performance and value. Meticulously maintained and showing clear evidence of responsible ownership, this unit offers a refined driving experience and mechanical integrity. It represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a high-caliber vehicle that remains in commendable condition both aesthetically and operationally.",
      "price": 36450.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
