      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in wonderful shape! It\u2019s been super dependable for me, runs like a dream, and has been really well-loved. It\u2019s clean, comfy, and honestly just a joy to drive. I\u2019d love for it to go to a great new home where it\u2019ll be appreciated. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
