    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies. The high-revving powerplant is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a limited-slip variable M differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory-tuned geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers for precise turn-in. While showing minor signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain exceptionally sharp.",
